{"type": "article", "id": 30229, "title": "买张“小床”，让辛苦工作的海绵睡上一觉｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-07-27T22:58:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 30732, "name": "Skinners Technologies"}, {"id": 30733, "name": "Harow"}, {"id": 30734, "name": "Hamilton Perkins"}, {"id": 30735, "name": "Solight"}, {"id": 30736, "name": "wishlist"}, {"id": 30564, "name": "OTOTO"}, {"id": 30737, "name": "Jenny Pokryvailo"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160804171100r6M3yYmn1g82sFTJ.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Skinners by Skinners Technologies</h3><p>鞋子的款式和功能越来越多，市面上更是出现了不少专门为增强运动表现而设计的鞋子。美中不足的是，有些鞋子可能过多地考虑专业性而牺牲了舒适和轻便。Skinners Technologies 的设计师们为此特别研发了一款介于鞋与袜之间的出行装备 Skinners，底部采用了极耐磨的双层材料，只要穿上它就可以照常进行健身、远足、以及其他锻炼活动。Skinners 仅重 80 克，可以像袜子一样卷起后塞进包里，让你在外出旅行时不用再背着又重又占地方的鞋子。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/skinners-revolutionary-ultraportable-footwear#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价为 40 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230152LAklubXUsPdBMVt6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607272301526y0D3WRa4BVb8XoS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.488235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230152W3fgbSF9IKZTesUG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.488235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230153xqFWM5wHLPyEolVr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.488235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230153A7cMZKsarYqDTFHw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.488235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230153lrxc2Xq9ZKWPoRfO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Iceberg by Harow</h3><p>炎炎夏日，由法国设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.harow.fr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Harow</a> 推出的矮桌 <a href=\"http://www.harow.fr/iceberg.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Iceberg</a> 或许会让你感受到一股凉意。这些方方正正的矮桌有着如同冰块一样光滑的表面，采用玻璃纤维和环氧树脂手工制作而成，Harow 希望通过这个独特的创意“冻结”住极地那种深邃的美感，同时展现出人类活动对于环境以及子孙的影响。Iceberg 均在位于巴黎的工作坊内进行加工，每一件都至少要花费一个月的时间，限量 100 件出售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230130qJdPa74CQ9tHXFWe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230130hv1EQjSl0ioCJgsR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230131JMTbjkV1HY0dEN7w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230130jP91eJoViyswqKWN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607272301312UuCG1tD0A3cw9rE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Hamilton Perkins by Hamilton Perkins Collection</h3><p>单从外观来看，这款名为 Hamilton Perkins 的拎背两用包和市面上同类产品并没有什么太大的区别，但它所使用的原材料可能会让你惊叹于它的环保程度：整体采用回收的塑料瓶制成，内衬所使用的乙烯基塑料则来自废弃的广告牌，因此每一个包都是独一无二的。所有两用包均在位于海地的工作坊加工生产，这种特殊的制作模式不仅降低了二氧化碳的排放，也为当地人提供了工作机会。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/26334503/hamilton-perkins-collection-from-plastic-bottles-t/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 95 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230110aRCI67QBvTb8lmgd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230110r2xSlRmtbjFV5KGQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607272301091kSBFsGHCuZ6OA3b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230110R8rVYZQnAk3c7PEi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230110E8oY4ZpKkfOBR7n6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230111koLE9XFKA4Op3uJY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Solar Puff by Solight</h3><p>当人们把“柔软”和“灯光”联系在一起时，通常表达的是光线的明暗。不过用它来形容 <a href=\"http://www.solight-design.com/#solarpuff\" rel=\"nofollow\">Solight</a> 这款名为 Solar Puff 太阳能灯具的话，就是真的在说它摸上去非常柔软了。这些小巧的正方体灯具由织物制成，能够压成厚度仅为 6 毫米的薄薄一片，便于随身携带。灯具上方设有太阳能板，在阳光下充满 8 小时之后能够连续使用 8 到 12 小时。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.solight-design.com/storeall/solarpuff\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 30 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230051VCW1ErDAu6NB9g53.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607272300515qn23oH6BACPUvdj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230051NaFAWOriedQExP5y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230052vejU6Lsro9EihHOn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230052cCyAWLHlhXTJZ0jF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Mon Cherry by Jenny Pokryvailo</h3><p>以色列设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/jennye589\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jenny Pokryvailo</a> 曾经为家居用品品牌 <a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OTOTO</a> 设计过一款尼斯湖怪造型的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/5660.html\">勺子</a>，今天要介绍的 Mon Cherry 是她的最新作品。Mon Cherry 由四颗独立的“樱桃”和一片“绿叶”构成，“樱桃”可以用作量勺，“绿叶”则是一个分蛋器。用这么一款可爱的厨具组合来制作蛋糕，心情似乎也变得更加愉快。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/collections/kitchen/products/mon-cherry-measuring-spoons-and-egg-separator\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 16 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230000CTNrMZPyj0RQnzs6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708478\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230001KUzeoMJt2kTC4lDP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607272300019YaQtFdBR42lqvxi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.434167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727225959HJz9uimjgckyxYbP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.752556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727230002wra8U75XkSc2pd9J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.807107\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Clean Dreams by wishlist</h3><p>将每个碗碟刷洗干净之后，辛苦工作的海绵也到了要上床休息的时候：这个名为 Clean Dreams 的“海绵床”是双人设计组合 <a href=\"http://www.wishlist-design.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">wishlist</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OTOTO</a> 设计的一款海绵支架。这件微型家具由塑料制成，可以放进洗碗机中清洗。床架的功能与肥皂盒类似，能够储存海绵滴下的水分。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/collections/kitchen/products/copy-of-button-up-magnetic-holders\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 15 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727225942vnhrwJ3QcCKxTAEu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.673594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607272259439xd8RQsNXvz6OjKf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.691932\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727225943J0yeqFHzXA5IQS3v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727225943cZlx3uiktXRFwIsP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.710269\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607272259430no7ImUM1kHzGSYq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800733\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}